job_descriptions: Full Stack Developer needed. Must have React, Node.js, and JavaScript experience. TypeScript knowledge preferred. We are building modern web applications using Next.js and MongoDB. Ideal for recent graduates with strong full-stack skills.

Machine Learning Engineer position. Required skills: Python, Scikit-learn, Numpy, Pandas. Experience with data analysis and AI models essential. Graduate role available for candidates with academic ML background.

Frontend Developer role. React.js and TypeScript required. Experience with Next.js, Tailwind CSS, and modern JavaScript frameworks. Looking for developer passionate about user interfaces and component design.
Backend Engineer needed. Node.js and database experience required. MongoDB or other NoSQL databases preferred. API development and RESTful services experience essential.
Junior Software Developer. Python or Java required. Experience with Git, agile methodologies, and team collaboration. Recent computer science graduates encouraged to apply. Training provided.
